\f0\b New Features, Bug Fixes and Other Progress since version 0.7.3\

\f1\b0 \'a5 Fixed item editing (including editing socketed gemstones, runes and jewels).\
\'a5 Added single-frame DC6 reading support.\
\'a5 Item editor displays images for most items (when the image name corresponds to the item's code).\
\'a5\'caChanged the item properties help button to point to my own website as Trevin's original page has been removed. Note that currently this webpage refers to properties from version 1.09, but that in the editor you will get the correct property description.\
